pipeline {
    agent any 

    environment {
        AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID     = credentials('access_key')
        AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY = credentials('secret_key')
    }
    
    stages {
        stage('checkout') {
            steps {
                git 'https://github.com/Vishwajeetkumar17/terraform-jenkis-project.git'
            }
        }
        stage('init') {
            steps {
                sh 'terraform init'
            }
        }
        stage('validate') {
            steps {
                sh 'terraform validate'                
            }
        }
        stage('plan') {
            steps {
                sh 'terraform plan'
            }
        }
        stage('action') {
            steps {
                sh 'terraform $action --auto-approve'
            }
        }
    }
}


for the variable 'action', go to 
configure -> general -> This project is parameterized -> 
select 'choice parameter' -> name it 'action' -> 
add choices 'apply', 'destroy' -> save the configuration.